name: CryptoNekos 03: ManeKollector
description:
Maneki Neko is a popular Japanese sculpture that brings luck, money and clients to its owner.

CryptoNekos is a syncretism combining the ancient Asian icon, with series of characters from Western pop culture.

In the NFTS world we are all looking for a piece of art that will attract money, and who better than the great Maneki Neko to do the job?

The sculpture in this animation is call ManeKollector. It's a tribute to one of the greatest heroes of my childhood, Super Mario, but above all it is a tribute to all NFTS collectors for making digital art possible.

Keep this CryptoNeko in your collection, and he will attract many cryptos for you!

more info and more CryptoNekos: https://www.cryptonekos.com/
